headline: Accenture Elevates Communications With Rachel Frey As Investors Weigh AI Story
summary: Accenture (NYSE:ACN) has appointed Rachel Frey as its first Chief Communications Officer. Frey will also join Accenture's Global Management Committee, expanding leadership representation for communications. The new role is intended to focus on company messaging, brand positioning, and the use of AI in communications.
